snippet.title: Twisted Metal: Black 2 - Harbor City Beta [Cancelled Game]
snippet.description:
Join us at: http://www.tmalliance.com
This video is of the long lost Twisted Metal: Black 2 that nearly completed development. This video contains footage from the beta version of the game.

More information at the following link: https://www.unseen64.net/2009/01/19/twisted-metal-black-2-harbor-city-ps2-cancelled/
Even more information:  http://chadliddell.tumblr.com/post/43227854671/did-you-know-the-above-image-is-a-screen-shot

The first level seen in the below video is  "Ghetto"
Around 2:40 you'll notice the game has it's own built in "Tweak Menu"
The second level "Goth" is shown at 3:58
The third level "Railyard" is shown at 6:34
The fourth level "SCenter" is shown at 8:54
The fifth level "Docks" is shown at 12:18
The rest of the video is a quick demo of all of the currently working vehicles.
